                    #KNAP0482
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

            <div class="p-5 border-2 border-blue-500 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center space-y-4 relative min-h-[180px]">
